headline: 2 No-Brainer Dividend Stocks to Buy for Income This May
summary: NextEra Energy has grown its dividend at a 10% compound annual rate over the past 20 years.  Realty Income has increased its dividend 130 times since its public market listing in 1994.  NextEra Energy (NYSE: NEE) and Realty Income (NYSE: O) are two such dividend stocks.
